sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: Promoter, RBS, HlyB, RBS, HlyD, Term
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Composite part for high levels of production of the HlyB and HlyD membrane proteins
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Alex Hatch

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_B1006
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: modified E. coli thr terminator, replaced all A-T pairs in stem with C-G pairs
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Artificial terminator, estimated %T~>90% *8bp stem, 6nt loop *Bidirectional, estimated reverse %T~>90%
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: Bidirectional, with the reverse estimated to be less effective than the forward. Has a polyA tail of 9 residues.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Haiyao Huang

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_M1003
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Membrane protein involved in type I secretion.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: Codon optimized for expression in E. coli while avoiding the BioBricks standard restriction sites.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Alex Hatch

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_M1004
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Membrane protein involved in type I secretion. When protein is fused to the HlyA signal peptide, this protein aids in protein secretion.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: Codon optimized for expression in E. coli while avoiding BioBricks standard restriction sites.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Alex Hatch

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_M1005
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Constitutive promoter with high transcriptional levels reported. RBS has high level of translation.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Alex Hatch
